Interface AssetConfiguration.AssetVarianceConfiguration

  • Enclosing interface:
    AssetConfiguration
    @ConfigurationProperties("gust.assets.vary")
public static interface AssetConfiguration.AssetVarianceConfiguration
    Describes settings that control the Vary header affixed to assets.
